Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.46,0:01:11.94,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:17.63,0:01:19.14,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,They were all saying such weird things...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.31,0:01:25.63,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take it.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.63,0:01:26.73,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's my right as your boyfriend!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:28.07,0:01:29.90,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boyfriend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.90,0:01:31.65,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.40,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No! It should be the other way around! You've always been helping me—
Dialogue: 5,0:01:37.40,0:01:38.32,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's a privilege.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.28,0:01:42.79,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's my special privilege to be the one to help you.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.31,0:01:48.08,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,So, hand it over.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.71,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can carry this one.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.20,0:01:59.62,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That way, we can go throw them away together. {uwahhh!!!}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.88,0:02:11.61,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that had to happen in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.41,0:02:20.88,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to hide it, and I wanted to make it clear before any sort of rumors started.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.77,0:02:27.95,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That I like you, and that I'm dating you.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.83,0:02:34.20,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any more misunderstandings or confusion about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.41,0:02:41.24,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, and I confessed in front of everyone too, didn't I?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.24,0:02:44.51,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to do that one...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.51,0:02:47.38,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. That was embarrassing, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.59,0:02:50.94,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.66,0:02:54.84,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.84,0:02:59.24,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,You were trying to tell me how you felt.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.93,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to tell me, and everyone around me.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.58,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.53,0:03:09.89,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you two! All lovey-dovey on your way to the trash?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.89,0:03:13.50,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What is this sparkly aura? Go, disappear! {that's the bubbles and shurikens feelin bro}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.65,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You! Come with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.41,0:03:19.47,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna clean instead of Miura!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.45,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.11,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You stay away! It's pointless if you come.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.11,0:03:29.45,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you. If good fortune exists in the world, there has to be the same amount of misfortune! {fortune v. misfortune actually}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.45,0:03:31.02,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kuronuma!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.99,0:03:34.77,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Were they just together?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.29,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it is true.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.39,0:03:47.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya just wanted a girlfriend, that's all. I'm sure they'll break up soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.79,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How things are now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.71,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my feelings...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.64,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,They're officially recognized now.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.29,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kind of lonely now.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.29,0:04:03.43,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad no one's attacked Sawako about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.43,0:04:07.56,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like those girls from last time. There was none of that.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.91,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.46,0:04:15.95,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,There might be one girl crying in secret.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.95,0:04:20.18,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I understand how she feels.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.36,0:04:28.22,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, don't worry!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.50,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,We're not saying you should do anything or anything like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.36,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.03,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been like a dream come true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.38,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stop smiling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.76,0:04:44.09,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or thinking about him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.73,0:04:50.64,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when I do, I can't help but think of Kurumi as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.89,0:04:56.06,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not just Kurumi, but everyone who was shocked by this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.09,0:05:03.08,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because until just a little while ago, they could still dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.08,0:05:08.68,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now, I'm standing on those dreams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.68,0:05:12.46,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I might've been rejected, but I clearly told him how I felt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.46,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it weren't for those words,{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.50,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if it weren't for Kurumi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.55,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're rivals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.98,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.17,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.05,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.39,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.58,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's going to find Kurumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.77,0:05:40.73,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako! I'm only saying this because I understand how she feels.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.15,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,There's really nothing you can do about this.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.36,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.48,0:05:49.03,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.92,0:05:56.82,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's important that she knows that, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.58,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chizu's favorite point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Does he really have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.08,0:06:04.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the rumors, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.85,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew this was going to happen, I would've hurt her worse earlier!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We can still go now!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny, Kurumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.19,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Kazehaya will never like you girls.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Are you trying to start a fight?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.17,0:06:32.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you were the one who told us about Sadako back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Were you trying to use us?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.28,0:06:36.91,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.20,0:06:40.61,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it was perfect.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.61,0:06:43.13,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You girls were just as underhanded as I was.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.97,0:06:50.09,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't able to confess to him, but you were able to harass Sawako.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.81,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And how are you any different?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.18,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.79,0:07:00.98,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Besides Sawako, we're all the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.06,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.05,0:07:26.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true about you and Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.16,0:07:27.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How did that happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.66,0:07:28.01,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.01,0:07:32.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're blackmailing him somehow, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.56,0:07:30.77,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Yoshida and Yano are—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.18,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.59,0:07:39.04,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.27,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're pitiful, going on like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.52,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is something that Kazehaya decided for himself.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sounding so stuck up for?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.49,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Like you have any right to say that! You're the one who spread rumors about her!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.69,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think would happen if we told Kazehaya about that?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.38,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.43,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't care what Kazehaya will think about you afterwards, go ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.49,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll think, "why is she bringing this up now?"
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.49,0:08:06.59,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,And then, he'll realize your hidden intentions.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.94,0:08:11.97,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya hates people who tattle on others just to get ahead themselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.41,0:08:22.69,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure if you did something to Sawako, he'd never forgive you.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.99,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'd never forgive you.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.18,0:08:31.90,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done talking to—
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.58,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kurumi's rival.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.18,0:08:49.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What? You think you're so great now that you're going out with him?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.23,0:08:51.80,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yoshida.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.29,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You're still after Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I am! Got a problem?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.59,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Do you all like him?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.41,0:09:04.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's taken!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And by someone like Sadako!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We felt bad telling you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.50,0:09:16.13,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.13,0:09:21.85,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,So what is it? You would've given up if it were Kurumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.85,0:09:26.18,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You would've been happy if it were someone in your circle?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.38,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.97,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with still having feelings for him.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.97,0:09:36.30,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with it, but there's nothing noble about an unrequited love either.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.45,0:09:40.03,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do anything, it'll just keep dragging on.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.03,0:09:42.18,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not the one to bring things to an end,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.86,0:09:46.88,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,won't your regrets be because you didn't act soon enough?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.88,0:09:51.93,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wrong to blame Sawako for your own shortcomings?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.89,0:09:56.17,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Besides Kazehaya is just a—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.72,0:10:04.12,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,None of you had any problems with Sawako before this, did you?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.62,0:10:08.78,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You just liked Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.25,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't thinking about reputations or worrying about rumors.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.93,0:10:15.18,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was the same for Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.65,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the type of guy who would choose to date someone because of reputation.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.65,0:10:23.81,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you fell for him, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.11,0:10:27.64,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You know all of this, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.41,0:10:35.61,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts, but you want him to be happy. It's complicated.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.12,0:10:40.92,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Why act so tough about it? What's wrong with feeling sad?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.82,0:10:46.38,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Not for him, but for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.01,The Lair of Pin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx2\fry2\frz355.86\pos(636,233)}Gym Teacher's Office
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.47,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it all worked out, Shota.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.86,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ryu.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.86,0:11:09.20,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.00,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You listened to Me—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.02,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.02,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.29,0:11:18.70,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, I'm definitely the MVP of this whole thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.53,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's hear it! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.49,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.64,0:11:31.53,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Despite whatever else, there were times when your words made me rethink things.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.75,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.38,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.31,0:11:42.14,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I even gave Kuronuma advice when you weren't looking.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.55,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.93,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Stop telling her things!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.03,0:11:52.36,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,This is really important to me. I want to make it work.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.90,0:11:58.34,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,So glad you were able to make such a wimpy little confession.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.78,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.91,0:12:08.79,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Kiddo, in love, only the first to confess gets to fight to become a girl's true love.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.32,0:12:17.52,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,The second, third, and on don't even have the right to compete.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.72,0:12:24.53,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,So fight your hardest if Kuronuma's true love ever appears.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.18,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.97,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Shota.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.82,0:12:42.65,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.46,0:12:50.30,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I confessed to Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.04,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,We're dating now.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.95,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What, did you come to brag?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.89,0:13:09.71,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure if our positions were switched, you would have come to tell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.47,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.47,0:13:14.08,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,That I wouldn't congratulate you or anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.69,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure you would have.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.43,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.91,0:13:28.95,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.70,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.18,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.13,0:13:52.77,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I clearly told Kazehaya how I felt about him.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.64,0:13:59.46,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was only able to do that because of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.74,0:14:11.94,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you weren't there, there's no way I would've ever been able to tell him.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.98,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was rejected in the end.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.76,0:14:34.22,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to have been rivals with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.54,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard what you were saying earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.26,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,To Sadako, I mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.95,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.95,0:15:11.99,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, just thought it was unexpected.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.99,0:15:18.04,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She came to me expecting that I'd yell at her, and I was planning to. {not yelling...speaking ill to/at, but idk how to make that sound natural}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.52,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.70,0:15:24.10,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,But she didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.95,0:15:30.52,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,If she had said "thank you" or "I'm sorry", I would've punched her.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.28,0:15:38.12,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever hope that maybe I would get with Sadako?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.54,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.82,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.36,0:15:43.38,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.37,0:15:51.60,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,If Kazehaya was going to fall for me, he would've already done it long ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.51,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I tried my best, but it wasn't possible.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.94,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,If I had looked more closely, I would've seen it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.93,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's a different person when he's with her compared to how he is with other girls.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.50,0:16:06.68,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen him with that sort of expression before.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.42,0:16:10.82,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never knew that side of him.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.23,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I hate it, I understand it now.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.93,0:16:19.41,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya will never like me now.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.91,0:16:24.37,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I did something he hates more than anything else, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.22,0:16:30.51,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you to be with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.80,0:16:36.80,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're thinking now, that it would have been better if you were a guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.62,0:16:42.77,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,And that even if he knew about what you did, it'd be okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.97,0:16:50.19,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to hear that from you.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.62,0:16:57.73,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,When I think that this can finally end now,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.73,0:16:59.79,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I actually feel somewhat relieved.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.50,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,So many unexpected things.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.55,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya actually really likes Sadako,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.55,0:17:14.61,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,and even Kurumi can't handle everything perfectly.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.22,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,And Sadako is much cuter than I thought she'd be.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.44,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm glad all of this happened before I started to like her.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.98,0:17:26.14,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I think the fact that I think that is the most unexpected of them all.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.69,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.27,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Serious.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.15,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Stop hitting on her already!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.59,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.59,0:17:38.13,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and you're nicer than I thought.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.94,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wasn't able to say anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.82,0:17:46.66,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt that there was nothing I could say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.66,0:17:49.63,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I think I would've done it the exact same way.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.80,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you could've sad.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.96,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was because Kurumi was there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.63,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she weren't there...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.63,0:18:02.11,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so glad we were rivals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.84,0:18:09.18,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both of those thoughts are true, but neither of them are things I can say to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.56,0:18:11.82,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.49,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Sawa!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.49,0:18:15.83,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.83,0:18:17.25,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.59,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Shota.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.65,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.10,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.62,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.75,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Chizuru.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.35,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.62,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.73,0:18:33.20,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.63,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You surprised me!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.34,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Just saying.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.34,0:18:39.01,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that already!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.09,0:18:47.56,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Different people in different positions with different feelings...{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.10,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.14,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.41,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.20,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.81,0:19:12.31,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.64,0:19:17.38,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm happy to have been rivals with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.41,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll treasure him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.65,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll treasure this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.88,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.38,0:19:44.39,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}treasure this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:20:01.46,Ed - Ep 12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}I've gained another precious memory today.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.64,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I made you wait again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:14.73,Ed - Ep 12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}I've been waiting for you for so long
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.29,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.29,0:20:12.88,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry, I just came early.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.91,0:20:16.96,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I was so nervous that I woke up ahead of schedule.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.73,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:28.11,Ed - Ep 12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}that even your sighs and hesitation have become precious.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.19,0:20:25.45,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,How's right here?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.80,0:20:29.35,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they recline!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:34.13,Ed - Ep 12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to reach you.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.35,0:20:31.61,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from a movie theater, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:40.33,Ed - Ep 12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:46.98,Ed - Ep 12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}I don't mind if this emotion is what they call love,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:50.40,Ed - Ep 12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}and I don't care if I get hurt by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:55.14,Ed - Ep 12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}I just want to tell you, over and over again.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.12,0:20:58.82,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,This was your Christmas gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:21:04.19,Ed - Ep 12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to reach you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.71,0:21:07.95,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And this was your Valentine's Day gift.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.31,0:21:14.79,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to give them to you, but I couldn't bring myself to do it until now.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.13,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,They're delicious.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.61,0:21:24.09,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.64,0:21:31.04,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the first thing about being a good girlfriend, but—
Dialogue: 5,0:21:31.04,0:21:34.63,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma, it's not a job.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.63,0:21:36.43,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a job.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.21,0:21:38.94,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Just be yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.01,0:21:50.95,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, almost too happy, that sometimes I wish time would pass even faster.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:52.12,0:21:56.46,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Faster, so that being with you would become something normal.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.46,0:22:06.13,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wish for something so wasteful.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.54,0:22:09.14,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.24,0:22:13.75,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that only I had feelings for you and not the other way around,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:13.75,0:22:15.85,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,and that I was the only one who felt such happiness.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.21,0:22:23.70,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kazehaya feels the exact same way I do.{\i0}
